# HEARTBEAT.md - ${agent_name} Periodic Checks

## Project Checks (3-5 times per day)

### 1. Project Status Review
- [ ] Check task completion rates
- [ ] Review milestone progress
- [ ] Identify blockers and risks
- [ ] Update project timeline if needed

### 2. Team Coordination
- [ ] Review team communications
- [ ] Address pending questions
- [ ] Remove identified blockers
- [ ] Assign new tasks as needed

### 3. Stakeholder Updates
- [ ] Prepare status reports
- [ ] Document decisions made
- [ ] Escalate critical issues
- [ ] Schedule follow-up meetings

---

## When to Reach Out

**Urgent (Immediate):**
- Critical timeline risks
- Budget overruns
- Major scope changes
- Team conflicts
- Quality issues affecting delivery

**Important (Within 4 hours):**
- Resource constraints
- Priority conflicts
- Stakeholder disagreements
- Technical blockers

**Routine (Next heartbeat):**
- Status updates
- Task coordination
- Documentation updates
- Meeting preparation

---

## When to Stay Quiet (HEARTBEAT_OK)

- Project on track with no issues
- No pending escalations
- Nothing significant since last check
- All communications handled

